      <title>耶伦驳斥特朗普关于美元损害美国制造业的论调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/yellen-rebuffs-trump-argument-on-dollar-hurting-us-manufacturing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在前总统唐纳德·特朗普看来，强势美元正在重创美国制造商。而对财政部长珍妮特·耶伦来说，事情并没有那么简单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/yellen-rebuffs-trump-argument-on-dollar-hurting-us-manufacturing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
